WEBVTT

00:07:58.262 --> 00:08:01.198
they look bright and shiny
and red and ripe.

00:08:02.284 --> 00:08:04.213
All of that effort,

00:08:04.237 --> 00:08:07.578
all of that agricultural
innovation and technology

00:08:07.602 --> 00:08:11.606
to create a product
that is entirely without taste.

00:08:12.388 --> 00:08:14.583
And onto the second tomato in our tale.

00:08:14.607 --> 00:08:16.923
This is the local version of the fruit.

00:08:16.947 --> 00:08:19.055
Its story is much, much shorter.

00:08:19.794 --> 00:08:23.744
This guy was grown by Luke Mahoney
and his family at Brookford Farm

00:08:23.768 --> 00:08:25.452
in Canterbury, New Hampshire.

00:08:26.028 --> 00:08:28.046
It's got a pretty boring backstory.

00:08:28.567 --> 00:08:30.072
